text: Erich Schultze (born 22 May 1890, date of death unknown) was a German swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Germany Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Berlin
